subject: Tell us how you‚Äôre doing!
html:
Dear %%NAME%%,

Hello from the USC Biofeedback Study! It has been about one year since you completed the 7-week heart rate biofeedback study at USC, and we would like to follow up with you. Below is a link to a consent form and a brief survey that should take no more than 10 minutes of your time to complete.

https://tinyurl.com/uscbiofeedback

If you complete the survey, you will be entered into a drawing to win a $100 Amazon gift card. A winner will be randomly selected for every batch of 50 participants who complete the survey.

Thank you for your time and we look forward to your responses!

The USC Biofeedback Study Team
